<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-31-0045 </DOCNO><TEXT>OPUS is a software package for selecting activation processes best suitedto an oil and gas field. It integrates an expert system which managesthe knowledge of the subject and organizes the implementation of a setof algorithmic programs for making technico-economic assessments. Thisarticle describes the expert-system part and gives an example of theuse of the complete system. 9 refs.</TEXT></DOC>